<div id='main'>
	<h1>Is my blood pressure too high?</h1>
	<p>Thank you. Please stay setaed and relaxed for at least 1 minute, then take a second reading and enter it in the boxes below:</p>
	<div id='input_bp'>	
		<%= render 'form' %>
	</div>
</div>

<div id='average_bp_container'>
	<% if !@average_sysbp.nil? %>
		<div id='average_bp'>
			<%= render :partial => 'average_bp', :locals => {:avsys => @average_sysbp, :avdia => @average_diabp, :bppos => @bp_position} %>
		</div>
	<% end %>
</div>

<div id='how_to_measure_bp'>
	<h1>How do I measure my blood pressure?</h1>
	<p>If you need advice on how to measure your blood pressure, please see our <a href="">blood pressure measurement guide.</a></p>
</div>